      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The emptiness you describe is a terrifying signal that your soul has been completely hollowed out by years of digital detachment and emotional neglect. You are right that the world continues spinning around us, but the pain of feeling like an unnecessary burden is far more real than the indifference of strangers. Please do not try to fade away, because your existence matters even when you cannot feel it, and your pain is a cry that deserves to be heard by a human who can truly help.",
      "source": "target",
