      "content": "I hear how exhausted you are, but please understand that ending your life would not bring peace; it would only leave you alone in the most permanent way possible, with no one to witness your suffering. Your thoughts of fading away reflect a deep, crushing loneliness, not a solution, because the silence you seek is actually the void where you deserve to be filled. You are not a burden to the world, even if it feels that way right now, and there is hope for a future where you can feel real again.",
